      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yee-haw~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0051695744,
      "endTime": 16.8829020182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0762353181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yee-haw~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0762353181,
      "endTime": 19.5300448178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.709569923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、来てくれてありがとう！\n千紗さんも参加してくれて嬉しいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for coming‚ Shizuku-chan!\nI'm glad Chisa-san could join too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.709569923,
      "endTime": 25.686395446400002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8762365896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、雫ちゃんに声を掛けてもらったから\n来てはみたけど……私で役に立てるかなぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah‚ I was invited by Shizuku-chan‚ so I came to see…\nBut… I wonder if I can be helpful?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8762365896,
      "endTime": 35.0515884955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2429032563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "この会議……暴走しがちなメンバー、多いから……\nすみれちゃんと一緒に……止めて、ほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this meeting… with many members prone to going off track…\nI'd like you and Sumire-chan… to help keep it on track",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2429032563,
      "endTime": 44.0694564104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2561229626
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、暴走しないように気をつけないとだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ you gotta watch out for not going off track‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2561229626,
      "endTime": 48.1356239874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3356239874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんですの？　あなたのことですわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? That's about you‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3356239874,
      "endTime": 52.0491614897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2358282327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私には荷が重いよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ I feel the pressure…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2358282327,
      "endTime": 55.5084587335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.7024948994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗さん、一緒に頑張ろうね……\nじゃあ、さとみさん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ch-Chisa-san‚ let's do our best together…\nThen‚ Satomi-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7024948994,
      "endTime": 61.8915878216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1024948994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　まずはみんなで自由に意見を\n出し合っていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! First‚ let's freely share our opinions together\nAlright‚ let's start brainstorming!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1024948994,
      "endTime": 66.84527499270001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.0358711482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうの、ブレインストーミングって\n言うんですよね！　頑張りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what they call brainstorming‚ right?\nLet's do our best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0358711482,
      "endTime": 72.1046013118,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12024.1288518
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3025378149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "では、まず言い出しっぺの私から……\n実は、アイデアだけなら沢山あるんです。ほら！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I'll start as the one who came up with the idea…\nActually‚ I have a lot of ideas. Look!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3025378149,
      "endTime": 79.939250652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1459172805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄い……！　この分厚い紙の束、もしかして\n全部アイデアメモですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Whoa…! Is this thick bundle of papers perhaps…\n…all idea notes…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1459172805,
      "endTime": 87.7738539298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9792506139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　気合いだけなら負けませんから！\nアイデア百本ノック、というやつです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I won't lose in terms of spirit!\nIt's the \"Hundred Ideas Knockout\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9792506139,
      "endTime": 94.0241866033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.2108534416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、アイデアがあり過ぎて、どれがいいのか\n分からなくなっちゃって……ぜひご意見を下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I have so many ideas that I'm not sure\nwhich ones are good… So please give your opinions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2108534416,
      "endTime": 102.1316550893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.2960481883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんの……アイデア、拝見します……\nほほぅ……これは、なかなか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see… Satomi-san's ideas…\nHmm… these are quite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2960481883,
      "endTime": 110.6239164591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.8372499069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "おっ、それが気になりますか、兵藤さん、お目が高い！\n一ノ瀬さんと井川さんの共演、見てみたいですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ interested in that? You have a discerning eye‚ Hyodo-san!\nYou'd like to see Ichinose-san and Igawa-san co-performing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8372499069,
      "endTime": 120.30000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5093827487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "こっちのアイデアも……ナイス。意外性が、ある\nでも私なら……ここに、芽衣ちゃんをひと匙……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This idea here… is nice. It has an element of surprise.\nBut if it were me… I'd add Mei-chan here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5093827487,
      "endTime": 130.3511965991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.5578634184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_02-stm008.m4a",
      "text": "おっ、そうきましたかー！\nそれなら私はここでさくらちゃんを起用します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ is that so!\nIn that case‚ I'll choose Sakura-chan for this role!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5578634184,
      "endTime": 136.563004486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
